Counter - blade technique
------------------------------------------------------------
As a swashbuckler increases in skill, he is able to exploit
openings left by an opponent's attack to strike a quick
counterattack. While using this skill, the swashbuckler will
counter a percentage of incoming attacks. This skill does
not provide any defense against the incoming attacks, only
allows the counterattacks.

GL:  9
SP:  15 / counterattack
command:  counter
duration: technique mode
